\section desc Description
<!-- Short description of what this package is supposed to provide -->

This package contain the classes estimating the pixel hit position and the respective errors. The EDProducers
read a SiPixelClusterCollection and store a collection of SiPixelRecHits.

\subsection interface Public interface
<!-- List the classes that are provided for use in other packages (if any) -->

- CPEFromDetPosition
- EtaCorrection
- PixelCPEBase
- PixelErrorParametrization
- SiPixelRecHitConverter

\subsection modules Modules
<!-- Describe modules implemented in this package and their parameter set -->

- SiPixelRecHitConverter Base EDProducer

\subsection tests Unit tests and examples
<!-- Describe cppunit tests and example configuration files -->

An example of configuration file is available in test/makeRecHits.cfg. An example for 
reading the pixel RecHit collection is given in test/readRecHits.cfg.

\section status Status and planned development
<!-- e.g. completed, stable, missing features -->
Stable. Roughly same functionality as in ORCA. Missing feature: correct position estimation for clusters including large pixels.

